  <description><![CDATA[<p>The lovely Hotel Francischiello Bellavista is set above the sea just 10 minutes' drive from Sorrento and <strong>close to the village of Massa Lubrense</strong>. The hotel offers fantastic panoramic sea views out towards the island of Capri from both the bedrooms and the rooftop gardens and terraces. Enjoy a drink on the terrace in the evening while watching the beautiful sunset over the Bay of Naples. The pool is situated on a terrace overlooking the sea and there is a heated pool in the indoor spa where there are a variety of treatments available.</p>]]></description>
